<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #080803;
        color: #cccccc;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #000;
        padding: 25px 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 100, 0.2);
    }

    h2, h3 {
        color: #a3be8c; 
        border-bottom: 2px solid #6a8f4c; 
        padding-bottom: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    form {
        margin-top: 15px;
    }

    label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    input[type="number"], input[type="text"], select {
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border: 2px solid #6a8f4c;
        border-radius: 4px;
        background-color: #2b2b2b;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 150px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

        input[type="number"]:focus, input[type="text"]:focus, select:focus {
            border-color: #a3be8c;
            outline: none;
        }

    button {
        margin-top: 15px;
        background-color: #6a8f4c;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        color: #121212;
        font-weight: bold;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #a3be8c;
        }

    .car-info {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

        .car-info p {
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

    .validation-summary-errors {
        color: #ff6b6b;
        background-color: #2a1a1a;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

    a.back-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 25px;
        color: #a3be8c;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

        a.back-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

    .top-bar {
        height: 140px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        background-color: #000;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        margin: 0 15px;
        color: #99ff00;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
        transition: color 0.3s;
    }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #6fa36b;
        }
</style>

<div class="top-bar">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="~/zdjecia/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 100px;" />
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Strona główna</a>
        <a href="/#samochody">Samochody</a>
        <a href="/Home/Kontakt">Kontakt</a>
        <a href="/Home/Opinie">Opinie</a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <h2>Opinie naszych klientów</h2>

    <div class="car-info">
        <p><strong>Mateusz K.:</strong> „Świetna obsługa, samochód był w idealnym stanie. Na pewno wrócę!”</p>
        <p><strong>Agnieszka L.:</strong> „Luksusowy wybór aut i bardzo konkurencyjne ceny.”</p>
        <p><strong>Piotr W.:</strong> „Profesjonalne podejście i szybki proces wypożyczenia. Polecam każdemu!”</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Dodaj swoją opinię</h3>
    <form>
        <label for="user">Twoje imię</label>
        <input type="text" id="user" name="user" required />

        <label for="opinion">Opinia</label>
        <textarea id="opinion" name="opinion" rows="4" style="width:100%; padding:10px; border-radius:5px; border:2px solid #6a8f4c; background-color:#2b2b2b; color:#e0e0e0;"></textarea>

        <button type="submit">Dodaj opinię</button>
    </form>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Powrót na stronę główną</a>
</div>
